sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant AD as Tenant Admin<br/>(admin panel)
    participant API as Admin API<br/>(tenant-scoped JWT)
    participant HOT as Audit trail (PII-FREE)<br/>DDB hot index 7d + Athena/S3 (retentionDays)
    participant ART as WebhookDeliveryArtifact<br/>exact sent bytes · CMK-enc · TTL replayRetentionDays
    participant WQ as webhook-q
    participant WH as Webhook λ
    participant EP as Tenant endpoint

    Note over AD,HOT: ① VISIBILITY — metadata only, PII-FREE, long-retained (50 days is fine)
    AD->>API: GET /v1/admin/webhooks/{id}/stats?from&to
    API->>HOT: 7d hot index = speed cache · older → Athena/S3 (retentionDays e.g. 365)
    API-->>AD: sent · delivered · failed · suppressed · success% ·<br/>p50/p99 latency · status-code breakdown · breaker state
    AD->>API: GET /v1/admin/webhooks/{id}/deliveries?from&to&type&status&cursor
    API-->>AD: per-attempt rows: notifId · type · ts · httpStatus · latency ·<br/>outcome · reason · replayable? (NO body — audit is PII-free)

    Note over AD,EP: ② REPLAY — re-send the EXACT bytes (no render · not from audit · not from DB payload)
    Note over AD: selection —<br/>{notifId} | {from,to} | {from,to, types:[X,Y], excludeTypes:[Z], status:failed}
    AD->>API: POST /v1/admin/webhooks/{id}/replay {…selection…, dryRun:true}
    API->>HOT: resolve selection → notifIds (Athena works 50d back)
    API-->>AD: DRY-RUN: count + how many still replayable vs expired (nothing sent)
    AD->>API: POST /v1/admin/webhooks/{id}/replay {…selection…, dryRun:false}
    API->>WQ: enqueue replay tasks (paced waves · replayId · idempotent notifId)
    WQ->>WH: receive
    WH->>ART: load stored artifact (the exact sent bytes)
    alt artifact within replayRetentionDays
        ART-->>WH: sent body (CMK-decrypted)
        Note over WH: NO renderer runs · refresh transport ONLY —<br/>Bearer(current) + HMAC over fresh-ts.body + X-CNS-Replay:true
        WH->>EP: POST verbatim body (content identical, auth/timestamp current)
        EP-->>WH: 2xx ⇒ audit webhook_replayed{delivered}
        Note over WH,EP: non-2xx ⇒ same retry → webhook-DLQ · consumer idempotent on notifId
    else artifact aged out (older than replayRetentionDays)
        Note over WH: still VISIBLE in the log, but replayable:false —<br/>audit replay_skipped:expired (raise replayRetentionDays to allow, at a PII-retention cost)
    end
